{"word":"G77 - ἀδάπανος - adápanos - ad-ap'-an-os - Without expense","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀδάπανος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">adápanos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ad-ap'-an-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Without expense</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"செலவில்லாமல், இலவசமாக - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"without expense, requiring no outlay"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G1160 - δαπάνη - dapánē - dap-an'-ay/1160\">G1160</a>; <i>costless</i>, that is, <i>gratuitous:</i> - without expense.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}